{"tid":1011446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國游說全球盟友及歐盟封殺華為參與5G建設","createTime":"2019-02-06T19:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T03:19:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c64dce2d1d7bf6cd35f1e20e1d48911ee78e5d2b","tid":1011446,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190206_20190206-182448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190206_20190206-182448.jpg&h=62ec875c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政府以存在安全隱患為由，游說全球盟友，特別是歐盟，在建設5G流動通訊網絡，不要使用華為等中國通訊製造商的設備。外電引述美國國務院官員說，美方人員正透過多種渠道，包括到布魯塞爾與北約盟友協商，又出席巴塞羅那及慕尼黑的國際會議，進行游說，敦促歐洲國家要顧及國家安全，不要急於與與來自中國等不可信賴的供應商，簽署合約。<br />\n<br />\n消息說，歐盟委員會正研究是否禁止華為參與5G建設工作，目前正處於初步階段，法國政府就說，會依據事實，決定5G競投，現階段未決定封殺華為；德國傳媒說，德國內閣將在今日召開閉門會議，研究華為，一旦參與德國5G建設，要採取的安全防範措施，會議將審議德國安全部門提交的安全目錄、牌照規範、及要求華為簽約承諾不能為中國政府收集情報。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1065333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1065333&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYAb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=bc665da8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1065333</a>"},{"pid":"fad5f6dde668e5ca7f58c2553f93507b89b81172","tid":1011446,"uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5167f6c8d56ced401132ed23c394b6a147d5f1e4","tid":1011446,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T00:08:07.000Z","msg":"歐盟班屎忽鬼所謂研究其實咪即係唔捨得支那啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41cabeb5e82b0cfbfbbdf175495abbfb1fe88b09","tid":1011446,"uid":34377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5167f6c8d56ced401132ed23c394b6a147